### Inventory Search API Tests (Port 3000)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### 1. Simple Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=intel
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Search with Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?category=Electronics
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. Search with Price Range
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?minPrice=100&maxPrice=500
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. Search with Multiple Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/search?q=hp&category=Electronics&minPrice=100&maxPrice=800
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json
